ed="T" n="0749a26"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0749a26"/><head><date from-iso="+0947-03-15" key="j20670182068464" to-iso="+0951-02-28">漢</date><placeName key="PL000000022578">棣州開元寺</placeName><persName key="A009942">恒超</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0749a27"/><persName key="A009942">釋恒<anchor xml:id="beg0749sgsz5"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>起</sic><corr>超</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0749sgsz5"/></persName>，姓馮氏，<placeName key="PL000000000368">范陽</placeName>人也。祖父不仕，世修<lb
ed="T" n="0749a28"/>儒道，而家富巨萬。<persName key="A009942">超</persName>生而聰慧，居童稚群，<lb
ed="T" n="0749a29"/>不貪戲弄。<date key="j20464922046856" from-iso="+0891-01-01" to-iso="+0891-12-31">年十五</date>，早通六籍<ptr type="glossary" target="#g32"/>，尤善〈風〉、〈騷〉<ptr target="#n1229"/>，辭<pb ed="T" n="0749b" xml:id="T50.2061.0749b"/><lb
ed="T" n="0749b01"/>調新奇，播流人口。忽一日因閱佛經，洗然開<lb
ed="T" n="0749b02"/>悟。乃歎曰：「人生富貴，喻等幻泡，唯有真乘，<lb
ed="T" n="0749b03"/>可登運載。」遂投<placeName key="PL000000002461">駐蹕寺</placeName>出俗。未周三祀<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1230"/>，<lb
ed="T" n="0749b04"/>方議進修，晝夜不疲，而屬師亡，亦遵釋氏<lb
ed="T" n="0749b05"/>喪儀，守禮無怠。孝悌之名，<placeName key="PL000000000368">燕</placeName>人所美。<date from-iso="+0913-02-14" key="j20545712054924" to-iso="+0914-02-02">梁乾<lb
ed="T" n="0749b06"/>化三年</date>，往<placeName key="PL000000005250">五臺山</placeName>受木叉戒<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1202"/>，由是陟遐自<lb
ed="T" n="0749b07"/>邇，切問近思<ptr type="glossary" target="#g490"/>。俄徵〈伐木〉之章<ptr target="#n1240"/>，且狎<anchor xml:id="beg0749sgsz6"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>或</sic><corr>成</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0749sgsz6"/>人之<lb
ed="T" n="0749b08"/>友<ptr type="glossary" target="#g284"/>，結契遠求名匠。阻<ref type="place" target="#PL000000023317 #PL000000001520">兩河</ref>間，兵未罷，路不<lb
ed="T" n="0749b09"/>通。南則<persName key="A003877">梁祖</persName>，北則<persName key="A006575">莊宗</persName>，抗衡於輕重之前，<lb
ed="T" n="0749b10"/>逐鹿在存亡之際。當是時也，<persName key="A009942">超</persName>止於<ref type="place" target="#PL000000000368">本州</ref><lb
ed="T" n="0749b11"/><placeName key="PL000000001522">魏</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000022310">博</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000003731">并</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000006220">汾</placeName>之間，學大小乘經、律、論，計七本<ptr target="#n1241"/>，講<lb
ed="T" n="0749b12"/>通<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1242"/>思，於<placeName key="PL000000042207">雍</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000023638">洛</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000043854">梁</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000025556">宋</placeName>名師，杳然隔絕。雖然，巡歷<lb
ed="T" n="0749b13"/>非遠，宏暢殊精，瓶滿見知，翼飛名字。是故<lb
ed="T" n="0749b14"/><placeName key="PL000000003731">并部</placeName><persName key="A009945">息塵</persName>、<placeName key="PL000000002511">中山</placeName><persName key="A009888">貞辯</persName>，夫二人者，言行俱臻，證<lb
ed="T" n="0749b15"/>修有位，一見<persName key="A009942">超</persName>，歎曰：「義龍之頭角<ptr type="glossary" target="#g532"/>悉完備<lb
ed="T" n="0749b16"/>矣，待飛奮而為霖雨焉！」其為碩德題目<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1243"/>，<lb
ed="T" n="0749b17"/>多此類也。<date from-iso="+0922-02-05" key="j20578492058202" to-iso="+0923-01-24">龍德二年</date>，挂錫於<placeName key="PL000000003128">無棣</placeName>，<persName key="A009942">超</persName>曰：「此<lb
ed="T" n="0749b18"/>則全<placeName key="PL000000020229">齊</placeName>舊壤，<placeName key="PL000000021567">鄒</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000021513">魯</placeName>善隣<ptr target="#n1244"/>。」遂止<placeName key="PL000000022578">開元</placeName>伽藍東北<lb
ed="T" n="0749b19"/>隅，置院講諸經論，二十餘年，宣導各三十<lb
ed="T" n="0749b20"/>餘遍。節操高邁，舉措舒徐<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1220"/>，緇素見之，無不<lb
ed="T" n="0749b21"/>怯懼。聲無叱咤，語不夸奢，自然而然，且非<lb
ed="T" n="0749b22"/>威勢凌𨏦<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1245"/>之所得也。前後州牧，往來使臣，嚮<lb
ed="T" n="0749b23"/>譽欽風，修名執刺<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1246"/>，相禮重者，止令童子辭<lb
ed="T" n="0749b24"/>以講貫<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1247"/>，罕曾接對。初有所慊，終伏其高，<placeName key="PL000000020229">齊</placeName>、<lb
ed="T" n="0749b25"/><placeName key="PL000000021513">魯</placeName>之間，造秀<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1248"/>不遠數百里，造其門以詰難。<lb
ed="T" n="0749b26"/>諸公一覩<persName key="A009942">超</persName>容，傍聽議論，參乎子、史，證以<lb
ed="T" n="0749b27"/>教宗。或問「因明」，<persName key="A009942">超</persName>答以詩一首，辭新理妙，<lb
ed="T" n="0749b28"/>皆悉歎降。時郡守<persName key="A009944">李君</persName>素重高風，欲飛章<lb
ed="T" n="0749b29"/>舉賜紫衣。<persName key="A009942">超</persName>聞驚愕，遂命筆為詩云：「虛著<pb ed="T" n="0749c" xml:id="T50.2061.0749c"/><lb
ed="T" n="0749c01"/>褐衣老，浮杯<ptr target="#n1249"/>道不成。誓傳經論死，不染<lb
ed="T" n="0749c02"/>利名生。厭樹遮山色，憐窓向月明。他時<lb
ed="T" n="0749c03"/>隨<persName key="A009388">范䗍</persName>，一棹五湖清。」<persName key="A009944">李君</persName>復令人勸勉，願<lb
ed="T" n="0749c04"/>結因緣。<persName key="A009942">超</persName>確乎不拔，且曰：「而其復爾，則<ref type="person" target="#A009942">吾</ref><lb
ed="T" n="0749c05"/>在<placeName key="PL000000001377">盧龍</placeName>塞外矣。」郡將聞而止。又相國瀛王<persName key="A009922"><anchor xml:id="beg0749sgsz7"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>憑</sic><corr>馮</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0749sgsz7"/><lb
ed="T" n="0749c06"/>道</persName>聞其名，知是鄉關宗人<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1250"/>，先遺其書，序以<lb
ed="T" n="0749c07"/>歸向之意。<persName key="A009942">超</persName>曰：「<ref type="person" target="#A009942">貧道</ref>閑人，早捨父母，剋<ptr type="glossary" target="#g374"/>志<lb
ed="T" n="0749c08"/>修行。本期<persName key="A001428">彌勒</persName>知名，不謂浪傳於<ref type="person" target="#A009922">宰衡</ref><ptr type="glossary" target="#g1251"/>之<lb
ed="T" n="0749c09"/>耳也。於<ref type="person" target="#A009942">吾</ref>何益？」門人敦喻，不得已而答書，<lb
ed="T" n="0749c10"/>具陳出家之人豈得以虛名薄利而留心乎？<lb
ed="T" n="0749c11"/><ref type="person" target="#A009922">瀛王</ref>益加鄭重，表聞<persName key="A006582">漢祖</persName>，遂就賜紫衣。自<lb
ed="T" n="0749c12"/>此忽忽不樂<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1252"/>，以<date when-iso="+0949-03-10" key="j20677442067744">乾祐二年仲春三日</date>微疾，<lb
ed="T" n="0749c13"/>數辰<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1253"/>而終于<ref type="place" target="#PL000000022578">本院</ref>。院眾咸聞天樂沸空，乃<lb
ed="T" n="0749c14"/>升<placeName key="PL000000055446">兜率</placeName>之明證也。春秋七十三，僧臘三十<lb
ed="T" n="0749c15"/>五。門人<persName key="A000792">洞<anchor xml:id="beg0749sgsz8"/>徵<anchor xml:id="end0749sgsz8"/></persName>與學徒百餘人持心喪<ptr type="glossary" target="#g837"/>，傾城<lb
ed="T" n="0749c16"/>士庶僧尼會送城外，具<anchor xml:id="beg0749sgsz9"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>茶</sic><corr>荼</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0749sgsz9"/>毘禮，收舍利二<lb
ed="T" n="0749c17"/>百餘顆分施之。外緘五十顆，於<ref type="place" target="#PL000000022578">本院</ref>起塔以<lb
ed="T" n="0749c18"/>葬之。<ref type="person" target="#A009922">瀛王</ref><anchor xml:id="beg0749003"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>未</sic><corr>末</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0749003"/>知，別奏賜師號曰<persName key="A009942">德正</persName>，乃<lb
ed="T" n="0749c19"/>刊勅文于石塔焉。</p>
